_sText:
A office style room, for fast battles, camping, etc...
Based on 1corridor, this map is slightly bigger and has different (better) doors and desks.
Map also contains several hidden features, for you to find out!
Screenies quality arent so good, just to lower filesize.

If you use this map on your server, please tell me, would be cool to know :)

Install at: C:\Program Files\Steam\your_user_name\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
